track.name: Gives You Hell
comments: And truth be told, I miss you and truth be told, I'm lying. [8]
This and "Move Along" are their best.   Amazingly catchy tune with a great beat and funny message.  One you can never tire of.
This song is going to be so timeless...

this song makes me smirk to myself <3
love it
When you see my face hope it gives You hell!
And truth be told, I miss you and truth be told, I'm lying. [7]
This is one of my favorite songs from them. This was a great song by them, its awesome.
And truth be told I miss you. And truth be told I"m lying :D!
And truth be told, I miss you and truth be told, I'm lying. [6]
Great song.  I never get tired of listening to it and I often sing along.

OMFG!!!! I havn't heard this song since I was in 4th grade! "Tomarrow you'll be thinking to yourself wher did it all go wrong?"  To my mother and every single pain in the butt who doesn't understand me! Nothing ever went wrong! I hope I give you hell!!!!
